> Its not legal to do reflect.DeepEqual on protos generated by newer protoc versions. 

I see changes to paths the might be hit by openapi serving code, which cares about equality (https://github.com/kubernetes/kubernetes/blob/master/staging/src/k8s.io/apiextensions-apiserver/pkg/controller/openapi/controller.go#L211-L213)

@sttts, do we have tests in place that would catch spurious detection of deltas

